message.body: Have you cooked up your bone yet? :)
your intuition is on point. I am about to sit down & eat bison marrow brown rice right now!!
Omg! That is so excellent!!! Enjoy it! When I did it, it turned on a primordial pilot light at my kidneys! I had never been warmer!!!
Yeah! We won't overload your blood my dear. Just some broth every other week?
